From Mike Sturdevant Subject Carrying crutches was Re Living In a previous article Don Fearn says When I broke my right leg in two places not a motorcycle accident a car accident who woulda thunk it I put my crutches on Gretchen's rear I'm getting the metal rod pulled out on Friday and going back on the crutches for six I think crutches on the handlebars sound more aesthetically How did you attach them When I got my knee rebuilt I got back on the street bike I put the crutches on the rack and the passenger seat and they hung out back a LONG Just make sure they're tied down tight in front and no Go Take Mike